==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Poussette
<hw>Pous*sette"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To perform a certain
movement in a dance.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Tennyson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Down the middle, up again, <qex>poussette</qex>, and cross.</q>
<rj><qau>J. & H. Smith.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pou sto</ent>⟦br⟧
